  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> are 20m<span>² and can sleep up to two people with double or twin beds. They have a bath or shower. This room type can be booked on request for sole occupancy at a supplement. </span></p>
<p><span><strong>New Standard Rooms</strong> are as above but newly renovated in a modern style with moquette or wood parquet. These rooms are available on request. </span></p>
<p><span><strong>Comfort Rooms </strong>are </span>25m² and sleep up to three people with a double or twin beds (the extra bed is a sofa bed). They have a bath with shower and a balcony.</p>
<p><span><strong>New Comfort Rooms </strong></span><span>are 30m² and recently renovated, they are smart and modern and sleep up to four people. They have a double or twin beds and a double sofa bed. They have a bath with hydro shower and have a balcony.</span></p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are 40m<span>² and sleep up to four people. The bedroom with double bed has sliding doors to the lounge area with a double sofa bed and seating area. These rooms are beautifully renovated with wood parquet. They have a bath with shower and a balcony. These rooms are available on request. </span></p>
<p><strong>Bedroom Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
